7
00:01:19,550 --> 00:01:20,590
你們別客氣  多吃點
Eat up, enjoy yourself.

8
00:01:24,290 --> 00:01:25,910
不好意思  打擾你們吃飯
Sorry to interrupt your dinner.

9
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:28,190
不要緊  我們到那邊坐吧
Never mind, let's sit over there.

10
